Horseshoe Crab Hour
Did you know the horseshoe crab was named after a giant one-eyed monster from Greek Mythology? You will learn all about the horseshoe crab's history, biology, and their importance to humans and 4th-10th other animals.
Current monitoring techniques used in Rhode Island will also be discussed.
